query:
UPDATE zsr_restreaming_backends SET
                name = $2,
                google_sheet_id = $3,
                language = $4,
                hth_export_id_col = $5,
                commentators_col = $6,
                trackers_col = $7,
                restream_channel_col = $8,
                notes_col = $9,
                dst_formula_standard = $10,
                dst_formula_dst = $11,
                updated_at = NOW()
            WHERE id = $1
